### Create Document with Items

POST {{Api_URL}}/api/Document
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "numeroDocumento": "PRE-001",
  "tipoDocumento": 1,
  "fecha": null,
  "estado": 1,
  "iva": null,
  "idCliente": "{{id_cliente}}",
  "items": [
    {
      "description": "Llaves de paso",
      "total": 500
    }
  ]
}

